[[模式種|模式種]]'''阿爾哈拉扇冠大天鵝龍'''（''Olorotitan arharensis''）於2003年由{{link-en|帕斯卡·古德弗伊|Pascal Godefroit}}等人所敘述、命名。屬名以[[拉丁語|拉丁語]]的''olor''（[[天鵝|天鵝]]）加上[[泰坦|泰坦]]，意即「巨大的天鵝」，象徵牠特別加長、多達18節頸椎的頸部。種名意指發現地來自阿爾拉哈縣（Arhara）<ref name=GBA03>{{cite journal |last=Godefroit |first=Pascal |author2=Bolotsky, Yuri |author3= Alifanov, Vladimir  |year=2003 |title=A remarkable hollow-crested hadrosaur from Russia: an Asian origin for lambeosaurines |journal=Comptes Rendus Palevol |volume=2 |pages=143–151 |doi=10.1016/S1631-0683(03)00017-4 |issue=2}}</ref>。中文名稱則由中國古生物學家[[邢立達|邢立達]]提出，以「扇冠」強調其特殊的頭冠形式<ref>{{cite web | author = 邢立達 | url = http://www.xinglida.net/Museum/Olorotitan.htm | title = 扇冠大天鹅龙 | website = 恐龙博物馆 | publisher = 中国恐龙网 | access-date = 2021-09-28 | archive-date = 2021-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210913082341/http://www.xinglida.net/Museum/Olorotitan.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[正模標本|正模標本]]'''AEHM 2/845'''是一副接近完整的骨骸，除了是俄羅斯第一次發現完整的恐龍化石，也是北美洲以外發現過完整度最高的賴氏龍亞科。1990年，俄羅斯[[布拉戈維申斯克|布拉戈維申斯克]]遠東礦產研究所的Vladimir A. Nagornyi，在[[遠東地區|遠東地區]][[阿穆爾州|阿穆爾州]]的{{link-en|昆杜爾|Kundur, Russia}}村莊附近的赤塔-哈巴羅夫斯克（Chita−Khabarovsk）高速公路沿線採集化石時，發現了這個挖掘地點。他立即通知布拉戈維申斯克地質探勘研究所。1999年起，在面積至少1000平方公尺的骨層展開挖掘活動，至2001年正模標本從岩石中完全挖出。<ref name=GBA03/>

當地屬於{{link-en|烏都赤坎層|Udurchukan Formation}}的一部分，年代約可追溯至白堊紀末期[[馬斯垂克階|馬斯垂克階]]。根據孢粉學證據顯示其詳細年代可能與[[美國|美國]]的[[地獄溪層|地獄溪層]]、{{link-en|蘭斯層|Lance Formation}}相仿，接近[[白堊紀﹣古近紀滅絕事件|白堊紀﹣古近紀滅絕事件]]。<ref>Nichols, D.J. and Sweet, A.R. 1993. Biostratigraphy of Upper Cretaceous non−marine palynofloras in a north−south transect of the Western Interior Basin. In: W.G.E. Caldwell and E.G. Kauffman (eds.), Evolution of the Western Interior Basin. Geological Association of Canada, Special Paper 39: 539–584.</ref><ref>Markevitch, V.S. 1994. Palynological zonation of the continental Cretaceous and early Tertiary of eastern Russia. Cretaceous Research 15: 165–177.</ref><ref name="Markevich 2001">Markevich, V.S. and Bugdaeva, E.V. 2001. Correlation of the Upper Cretaceous and Palaeogene plant−bearing deposits of the Russian Far East. In: E.V. Bugdaeva (ed.), Flora and Dinosaurs at the Cretaceous–Paleogene Boundary of Zeya−Bureya Basin (IGCP project 434), 76–96. Dalnauka, Vladivostok.</ref><ref>Nichols, D.J. 2002. Palynology and biostratigraphy of the Hell Creek Formation in North Dakota: a microfossil record of plants at the end of Cretaceous time. In:  D.J. Nichols (ed.),The Hell Creek Formation and the Cretaceous–Tertiary Boundary in the Northern Great Plains: An Integrated Continental Record of the End of the Cretaceous. Geological Society of America Special Papers 361: 393–456.</ref><ref>Nichols, D.J. and Johnson, K.R. 2008. Plants and the K−T Boundary . 280pp. Cambridge University Press, Cambridge.</ref>該地動物相與相隔一條[[黑龍江|黑龍江]]對岸、[[中國|中國]][[黑龍江省|黑龍江省]][[嘉蔭縣|嘉蔭縣]][[烏拉嘎鎮|烏拉嘎鎮]]的[[漁亮子組|漁亮子組]]連成一片<ref>Riabinin, A.N. 1930. ''Mandschurosaurus amurensis'' nov. gen. nov. sp., a hadrosaurian  dinosaur  from  the  Upper  Cretaceous  of  Amur  River. Mémoires de la Société paléontologique de Russie 2: 1–36.</ref><ref name="Godefroit2001">Godefroit, P., Zan, S., and Jin, L. 2001. The Maastrichtian (Late Cretaceous) lambeosaurine dinosaur ''Charonosaurus jiayinensis'' from north−eastern China. Bulletin de l’Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique, Sciences de la Terre 71: 119–168.</ref><ref name="Godefroit 2008">Godefroit, P., Hai, S., Yu, T., and Lauters, P. 2008. New hadrosaurid dinosaurs  from  the  uppermost  Cretaceous  of  northeastern  China. Acta Palaeontologica Polonica 53: 47–74.</ref>，為一個橫跨數百平方公尺的骨層，並盛產[[鴨嘴龍科|鴨嘴龍科]]，<ref>Bolotsky, Y.L. and Kurzanov, S. 1991. The hadrosaurs of the Amur Region. In: V. Moiseyenko (ed.), Geology of the Pacific Ocean Border, 94–103. Amur KNII, Blagoveschensk.</ref>包含[[阿穆爾龍|阿穆爾龍]]<ref name="Godefroit 2004b">Godefroit P., Bolotsky, Y.L., and Van Itterbeeck, J. 2004b. Amurosaurus riabinini , a Late Cretaceous lambeosaurine dinosaur from Far Eastern Russia. Acta Palaeontologica Polonica 49: 585–618.</ref>、[[卡戎龍|卡戎龍]]<ref>Godefroit, P., Zan, S., and Jin, L. 2000. ''Charonosaurus jiayinensis'' n.g., n.sp., a lambeosaurine dinosaur from the Late Maastrichtian of north−eastern China . Comptes rendus de l’Académie des Sciences de Paris, Sciences de la Terre et des Planètes 330: 875–882.</ref>、[[克貝洛斯龍|克貝洛斯龍]]<ref name=BG04/>、[[昆杜爾龍|昆杜爾龍]]<ref>Godefroit, P., Bolotsky, Y.L., and Lauters, P. 2012. A new saurolophine dinosaur from the latest Cretaceous of Far Eastern Russia. PLoS ONE 7 (5): e36849. doi:10.1371/jounal.pone.0036849.</ref>、[[黑龍江龍|黑龍江龍]]、[[滿洲龍|滿洲龍]]等；此外還有大量零碎、較小的單獨骨骼，可能屬於以上物種或扇冠大天鵝龍。<ref name="Godefroit2012">Godefroit, P., Bolotsky, Y.L., and Bolotsky, I.Y. 2012. Osteology and relationships of ''Olorotitan arharensis'' , a hollow−crested hadrosaurid dinosaur from the latest Cretaceous of Far Eastern Russia. Acta Palaeontologica Polonica 57 (3): 527–560.</ref>

